Build and install bashcritic

Install globally (root/superuser permissions needed)
====================================================

In the src directory run:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

Install locally
===============

In the src directory run:

    perl Makefile.PL PREFIX=${HOME}
    make
    make install

In this case files will be installed in ${HOME}/bin, ${HOME}/lib and
${HOME}/man
